26:48.084 --> 26:49.608
-GET BACK, MAN OR
I'M GONNA CUT YOU!

26:49.738 --> 26:51.871
I'M GOING TO SLICE
YOU INTO TOOTHPICKS!

26:52.001 --> 26:53.176
-NO WAY, MAN.

26:53.307 --> 26:54.830
NO WAY, THAT THING...

26:56.571 --> 26:58.704
THAT THING IS ABOUT TO RUN
OUT OF GA-- THAT THING...

26:58.834 --> 26:59.618
-CUT!

27:00.314 --> 27:01.794
-I'M SORRY, I FORGOT THE LINES.

27:01.924 --> 27:03.534
-NO, NO, DARLING, NOT
NOW, PLEASE. NOT NOW.

27:03.665 --> 27:04.971
-CAN I JUST DO IT ONE MORE
TIME? I'LL GET IT RIGHT.

27:05.101 --> 27:06.450
-IT'S NO PROBLEM.

27:06.581 --> 27:08.061
JUST TAKE IT ONE
LINE AT A TIME, OKAY?

27:08.191 --> 27:10.411
ALL RIGHT? WONDERFUL.

27:10.541 --> 27:12.065
-GREAT. GOT IT.

27:14.589 --> 27:16.678
AH! [LAUGHING]

27:16.809 --> 27:17.897
-FROM THE TOP.

27:18.027 --> 27:18.941
-FROM THE TOP.

27:19.812 --> 27:20.769
-MAN: OKAY, SETTLE.

27:22.205 --> 27:23.729
-NO WAY. NO WAY.

27:23.859 --> 27:25.208
-ALL RIGHT, LET'S ROLL.

27:25.339 --> 27:26.732
-NO WAY.

27:26.862 --> 27:28.647
-FERNANDO: SCREEN
TEST, MITCH BUCHANNON,

27:28.777 --> 27:30.561
TAKE 23.
-NO WAY. THAT THINGS ABOUT...

27:30.692 --> 27:33.260
-FERNANDO: AND...
-MOTIVATION.

27:33.390 --> 27:34.522
-FERNANDO: ACTION.

27:34.653 --> 27:36.611
[CHAINSAW RUNNING]

27:36.742 --> 27:37.873
-HEY, HARV, I GOT
TO TALK TO YOU.

27:38.004 --> 27:39.309
-NOT NOW. NOT NOW.

27:41.747 --> 27:43.836
-HOLD IT RIGHT
THERE, SCUZZBUCKET.

27:44.575 --> 27:45.751
-GET BACK, MAN OR
I'M GOING TO CUT YOU!

27:45.881 --> 27:47.317
I'M GOING TO CUT
YOU INTO TOOTHPICKS!

27:47.448 --> 27:50.059
-NO WAY. THAT THING'S
ABOUT TO RUN-- NO--

27:50.190 --> 27:53.149
-CUT! CUT! CUT!

27:53.715 --> 27:54.673
-COULD I TALK TO
YOU FOR A SECOND?

27:54.803 --> 27:56.326
-OF COURSE, MITCH.

27:56.457 --> 27:59.503
-DO YOU MIND IF WE DO THIS
WITHOUT THE SAW RUNNING?

28:00.156 --> 28:02.245
-WITHOUT THE SAW.

28:02.376 --> 28:03.551
WHAT A GREAT IDEA!

28:04.160 --> 28:05.901
WE'LL JUST PRETEND THAT
IT'S STILL RUNNING.

28:06.032 --> 28:07.642
-OK.

28:07.773 --> 28:09.078
-BUT I STILL WANT YOU TO
SHOW FEAR THAT THE BLADES

28:09.209 --> 28:10.732
ARE GOING TO SHRED
THIS BEAUTIFUL FACE.

28:11.298 --> 28:12.342
BUT ONLY BENEATH THE SURFACE.

28:12.473 --> 28:15.737
ON THE SURFACE YOU HAVE NO FEAR.

28:17.304 --> 28:18.479
PLAY THE SUBTEXT.

28:19.349 --> 28:20.524
-SUBTEXT.
-SUBTEXT.

28:21.177 --> 28:22.265
-SUBTEXT.

28:22.788 --> 28:24.137
-MOP HIM UP.

28:26.313 --> 28:27.531
LET'S DO IT AGAIN.

28:28.837 --> 28:30.317
HE DOESN'T WANT TO DO THIS.

28:30.447 --> 28:33.189
-JUST MAKE HIM LOOK GOOD.

28:33.320 --> 28:34.843
-SUBTEXT.

28:35.409 --> 28:37.237
WHAT THE HELL IS SUBTEXT?

28:37.367 --> 28:39.500
-HEY, LISTEN, I THINK I
KNOW HOW TO GET SPONSORS

28:39.630 --> 28:41.328
FOR THIS BIKINI
CONTEST OF YOURS.

28:42.242 --> 28:43.765
-WHAT? HOW? HOW?

28:44.723 --> 28:46.246
-HOW ABOUT A BENEFIT FOR ORCAS?

28:48.509 --> 28:51.860
-WHAT A CONCEPT.
HEY, I LIKE IT!

28:51.991 --> 28:53.122
IT'S--
-FERNANDO: SILENCE!

28:53.819 --> 28:55.168
[CLEARS THROAT]

28:55.298 --> 28:56.343
-TALK TO YOU LATER.

28:56.473 --> 28:57.779
-I'LL TALK TO YOU.
-OKAY.

28:57.910 --> 29:01.217
-LET'S ROLL. MITCH
BUCHANNON, TAKE 25.

29:02.523 --> 29:03.829
-SCUDBUCKET.

29:03.959 --> 29:05.134
-FERNANDO: AND...

29:05.265 --> 29:06.788
-JUST BE COOL, JUST BE COOL.

29:07.789 --> 29:08.659
-ACTION!

29:09.312 --> 29:11.880
-HOLD IT RIGHT
THERE SCUZZBUCKET!

29:12.011 --> 29:13.186
-SCUDBUCKET!

29:13.316 --> 29:14.230
-FERNANDO: CUT!

29:14.361 --> 29:15.841
-NO, NO! NO, KEEP ROLLING.

29:15.971 --> 29:17.320
-I'M SORRY.

29:17.451 --> 29:18.539
I'M SORRY. IT'S ALRIGHT.

29:18.669 --> 29:22.673
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

29:25.154 --> 29:26.112
[GRUNTING]

29:27.940 --> 29:30.943
-HOLD IT RIGHT
THERE, SCUDBUCKET.

29:31.073 --> 29:34.207
-MAN: HELP! HELP!
THIS GUY'S CRAZY, HELP US!

29:34.337 --> 29:35.338
[WOMAN SCREAMING]

29:36.644 --> 29:37.819
-HEY!

29:37.950 --> 29:38.864
LEAVE HER ALONE!

29:38.994 --> 29:40.387
-AH!

29:40.517 --> 29:43.085
[FIGHTING] [GRUNTING]

29:46.393 --> 29:48.787
[CRASH]

29:48.917 --> 29:50.527
-KEEP SHOOTING! KEEP SHOOTING!

29:56.533 --> 29:58.231
-AHH!

29:59.841 --> 30:00.711
-AH.

30:00.842 --> 30:01.843
-AH!

30:01.974 --> 30:03.366
[GRUNTS]

30:03.497 --> 30:05.194
-YEAH, ROLL.

30:05.325 --> 30:08.850
[FIGHTING] [GRUNTING]

30:08.981 --> 30:12.332
[INTENSE MUSIC]

30:35.964 --> 30:36.835
-UGH!

30:36.965 --> 30:38.358
AH.

30:48.498 --> 30:50.022
-GET HIM. COME ON, COME
ON, COME ON, COME ON.

30:53.329 --> 30:55.592
[GRUNTING] [FIGHTING]

30:58.465 --> 31:00.554
[CRASH]

31:01.337 --> 31:02.991
[SIREN WAILING]

31:03.122 --> 31:04.471
-OH!

31:04.601 --> 31:06.212
-YOU BETTER HAVE
THESE RIBS LOOKED AT.

31:06.342 --> 31:08.344
AND THAT FACE. LET ME SEE.

31:08.475 --> 31:11.870
I WANT MY LEADING MAN
TO BE IN PERFECT SHAPE.

31:12.000 --> 31:13.306
-THAT MEANS HE GOT THE JOB!

31:14.133 --> 31:16.048
-NOW, MAKE YOURSELF
USEFUL GO GET THAT CRAZY

31:16.178 --> 31:18.441
TO SIGN A RELEASE SO WE
CAN USE THIS FOOTAGE.

31:18.572 --> 31:19.573
-YOU GOT IT!

31:20.095 --> 31:23.272
-WELL DONE. WELL DONE.
YOU WERE TERRIFIC!

31:24.795 --> 31:25.796
-HEY, THIS LOOKS GREAT.

31:25.927 --> 31:27.537
-THANKS!

31:27.668 --> 31:28.495
-I'VE GOT SOME MORE
PROMOTIONAL PAMPHLETS INSIDE.

31:28.625 --> 31:30.410
-GREAT.

31:30.540 --> 31:31.977
-YEAH, I THINK YOU SIGNED UP
EVERY SURF SHOP AND RESTAURANT

31:32.107 --> 31:33.456
BETWEEN THE ORANGE AND
VENTURA COUNTY LINE.

31:33.587 --> 31:34.980
-YEAH, AND I GOT
JAG BATHING SUITS

31:35.110 --> 31:36.764
TO UNDERWRITE SOME
OF THE EXPENSES.

31:36.895 --> 31:38.418
I JUST HOPE THAT WE
GOT ENOUGH GIRLS.

31:38.548 --> 31:40.942
-ALL WE REALLY NEED IS
YOU, MY LITTLE RUMPUS ROOM.

31:41.073 --> 31:42.988
-OH NO, I'VE GOT A
MILLION THINGS TO DO

31:43.118 --> 31:44.772
IF I'M GOING TO GET
THIS PUT ON IN TIME.

31:44.903 --> 31:46.556
-HEY, HEY, I GOT A SLEW OF
LIFEGUARDS WHO ARE WILLING

31:46.687 --> 31:48.471
TO PUT UP A TON OF MONEY TO
SPONSOR ONE OF THEIR OWN.

31:48.602 --> 31:49.603
-WELL THEN, THEY'RE
JUST GOING TO HAVE

31:49.733 --> 31:50.909
TO GET ONE OF THEIR OWN.

31:52.780 --> 31:54.086
-WHO?

31:57.480 --> 32:00.135
[VOICE ON TV]

32:03.617 --> 32:05.140
[DEEP BREATH]

32:06.141 --> 32:07.142
[TURNS OFF TV]

32:09.144 --> 32:10.145
-OW.

32:11.146 --> 32:12.452
HMM.

32:15.846 --> 32:17.109
YOU TALKING TO ME?

32:18.632 --> 32:21.374
HEY! HEY, YEAH, YOU.

32:22.505 --> 32:23.854
YOU TALKING TO ME?

32:23.985 --> 32:25.378
-YOU'RE DOING YOUR HOMEWORK?

32:26.292 --> 32:28.120
UH, THE DOOR WAS OPEN.

32:28.685 --> 32:30.470
DON'T WORRY, I LOCKED IT.

32:37.172 --> 32:38.086
-HI.

32:38.652 --> 32:40.480
-I'VE JUST COME FROM
THE EDITING ROOM.

32:41.046 --> 32:45.615
HAS ANYONE EVER TOLD YOU
YOU HAVE THE BLUEST EYES?

32:46.181 --> 32:47.966
-I HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH THAT.

32:49.315 --> 32:51.752
-THE FIGHT SCENE IS FANTASTIC.

32:52.709 --> 32:55.364
I THINK WE SHOULD WORK ON MAKING

32:55.495 --> 32:59.760
THE LOVE SCENE
EQUALLY REALISTIC.

33:00.282 --> 33:04.504
-UM, UH, I GOT A
LITTLE BOY UPSTAIRS.

33:04.634 --> 33:06.071
-I WON'T MAKE A SOUND.

33:07.507 --> 33:08.943
-UM.

33:09.074 --> 33:12.599
-MM, I AM GOING TO
MAKE YOU A SUPERSTAR.

33:13.774 --> 33:17.691
-BUT, DITA, I DON'T THINK
THIS WAS PART OF THE DEAL.

33:17.821 --> 33:21.651
-WELL, CALL IT
AN ORAL AGREEMENT.

33:24.089 --> 33:28.180
MITCH, MITCH, DON'T
DISAPPOINT ME.

33:32.749 --> 33:34.229
-I'M SORRY.

33:35.622 --> 33:37.102
I THINK YOU BETTER LEAVE.

33:44.022 --> 33:45.806
-YOU'RE NOT BEING
VERY SMART, MITCH.

33:46.328 --> 33:49.201
-NO, I KINDA THINK THIS
IS THE SMARTEST THING

33:49.331 --> 33:51.594
I'VE DONE SINCE I GOT
INVOLVED IN THIS MESS.

33:53.248 --> 33:54.554
-ALL RIGHT.

34:00.908 --> 34:02.257
YOU'RE GOING TO REGRET THIS.

34:03.998 --> 34:04.912
-MAYBE I WILL,

34:06.609 --> 34:08.176
BUT I'LL LIVE WITH IT.

34:11.701 --> 34:13.051
[DOOR CLOSING]

