36:39.675 --> 36:40.459
-I COULDN'T.

36:40.589 --> 36:41.503
-BUT SHE'S A FOX.

36:41.634 --> 36:43.026
-OH, THAT'S NOT THE POINT.

36:43.157 --> 36:45.986
-WAIT A MINUTE. WERE YOU
FIRED, OR DID YOU QUIT?

36:46.508 --> 36:48.075
-I THINK I WAS FIRED.
WHAT'S THE DIFFERENCE?

36:48.206 --> 36:49.729
-BUT YOU SIGNED THE
CONTRACT THOUGH, DIDN'T YOU?

36:49.859 --> 36:50.904
-YEAH.

36:51.557 --> 36:55.430
-YES! PAY OR PLAY,
BABY! PAY OR PLAY!

36:55.561 --> 36:56.953
