36:57.084 --> 36:58.781
IT'S FEEDBACK, THAT'S
MY CUE. GOT TO GO!

36:59.695 --> 37:01.567
PAY OR PLAY, YES!

37:05.048 --> 37:08.095
[APPLAUDING, CHEERING]

37:14.232 --> 37:15.668
-WHAT DO YOU THINK?

37:15.798 --> 37:16.886
L.A. COUNTY'S GOT THE
BEST-LOOKING WOMEN?

37:17.017 --> 37:19.585
[AUDIENCE AGREEING]

37:19.715 --> 37:22.631
[AUDIENCE APPLAUDING]

37:27.070 --> 37:29.725
WELL, IF I COULD HAVE JUST
ONE MINUTE OF YOUR TIME,

37:29.856 --> 37:31.727
I WANT TO TELL YOU THAT
WE ALSO HAVE A VERY

37:31.858 --> 37:34.077
IMPORTANT ENVIRONMENTAL
RESPONSIBILITY TO UPHOLD.

37:34.208 --> 37:36.036
EVERY YEAR, THOUSANDS
OF SEA MAMMALS

37:36.166 --> 37:37.690
NEED MEDICAL
TREATMENT TO SURVIVE

37:37.820 --> 37:38.952
AND THEY'RE NOT
GETTING ENOUGH HELP,

37:39.082 --> 37:40.823
SO PLEASE SPEND SOME MONEY.

37:40.954 --> 37:43.173
PICK YOUR FAVORITE GIRL
AND BACK HER WITH SOME CASH

37:43.304 --> 37:44.740
SO THAT WE CAN KEEP ORCAS OPEN,

37:44.871 --> 37:46.394
AND THAT'S ALL I HAVE
TO SAY, THANK YOU.

37:46.525 --> 37:47.569
[AUDIENCE APPLAUDING]

37:47.700 --> 37:51.138
[AUDIENCE CHEERING]

37:51.269 --> 37:55.098
-HEY, COME ON! COME
ON! SHUT UP! SHUT UP!

37:55.229 --> 37:57.405
WHY YOU CLAPPING? I'M
NOT WEARING A BIKINI!

37:57.536 --> 38:00.408
WELL, ALL RIGHT, I'M
WEARING A BIKINI.

38:00.539 --> 38:03.629
UNDERNEATH THIS SHIRT
AND THESE SHORTS

38:03.759 --> 38:09.243
I AM WEARING A TEENY,
TINY PAIR OF BRIEFS.

38:09.374 --> 38:17.120
IT'S NOT A PRETTY SIGHT, BUT
SINCE MY LIFEGUARD BUDDIES

38:17.947 --> 38:20.689
HAVE CHOSEN TO SPONSOR ME,

38:23.475 --> 38:25.477
YOU GUYS BETTER COME
UP WITH SOME BUCKS

38:25.607 --> 38:28.088
IF YOU WANT YOUR CONTESTANT
TO WIN BECAUSE, FOLKS,

38:28.741 --> 38:31.657
THIS IS STRICTLY PAY-PER-VIEW.

38:31.787 --> 38:33.789
[AUDIENCE CHEERING]

38:33.920 --> 38:37.097
ALL RIGHT, OKAY,
NOW IT'S TIME NOW

38:37.227 --> 38:39.404
FOR THE FINAL
CONTESTANT SHOWDOWN.

38:39.534 --> 38:41.536
LADIES, STRUT YOUR STUFF.

38:41.667 --> 38:44.452
[AUDIENCE CHEERING]

38:44.583 --> 38:47.020
[INSTRUMENTAL MUSIC]

38:57.552 --> 38:58.945
[AUDIENCE CHEERING]

38:59.075 --> 39:00.773
[WOLF-WHISTLING]

39:00.903 --> 39:02.427
OKAY, NOW IT'S TIME TO ANNOUNCE

39:02.557 --> 39:04.429
THE WINNER OF OUR COMPETITION.

39:04.559 --> 39:05.865
THIS WILL BE THE CONTESTANT WITH

39:05.995 --> 39:08.346
THE MOST MONEY
PLEDGED ON HER BEHALF.

39:08.476 --> 39:13.089
AND THE WINNER IS,
ENVELOPE PLEASE. THANK YOU.

39:13.220 --> 39:19.618
WITH A GRAND TOTAL
OF $5,137, HAR...

39:20.488 --> 39:22.055
-HARVEY MILLER!

39:22.185 --> 39:24.666
[CHEERING]
-WHOO! WHOO!

39:24.797 --> 39:26.668
[APPLAUDING]

39:26.799 --> 39:31.369
BUT THE REAL WINNER IS
THE ORCAS FOUNDATION

39:31.499 --> 39:36.983
WITH A GRAND TOTAL
OF $32,000! WHOO!

39:37.636 --> 39:39.115
[SEA LION BARKING]

39:40.595 --> 39:43.511
-HELLO, SWEETIE. HI, GILLY.

39:43.642 --> 39:47.863
HOW ARE YOU TODAY? ARE
YOU FEELING BETTER?

39:48.647 --> 39:51.084
ARE YOU FEELING BETTER?
YOU LOOK SO PRETTY.

39:51.214 --> 39:53.260
HOW LONG BEFORE SHE
CAN BE RELEASED?

39:53.391 --> 39:55.131
-WELL, SHE'S REGAINED
A LOT OF STRENGTH.

39:55.262 --> 39:57.743
I THINK THAT WE CAN LET HER GO
BEFORE WE CLOSE UP TOMORROW.

39:59.788 --> 40:01.224
-I'M REALLY SORRY
IT WASN'T ENOUGH.

40:01.355 --> 40:03.401
-SHAUNI, RAISING
THIS MUCH MONEY

40:03.531 --> 40:05.446
ON SUCH SHORT NOTICE
WAS UNBELIEVABLE.

40:05.577 --> 40:07.970
-I KNOW. I KNOW. I JUST WISH
I WOULD HAVE KNOWN SOONER.

40:08.101 --> 40:09.363
YOU KNOW THERE WERE A
LOT OF CORPORATE PEOPLE

40:09.494 --> 40:11.104
THAT I DIDN'T GET TO WRESTLE.

40:11.234 --> 40:12.627
-HEY, WHAT'S HAPPENING?

40:13.802 --> 40:15.978
OH, NO. WHY ALL THE SAD FACES?

40:16.109 --> 40:16.979
-WE CAME UP SHORT.

40:17.110 --> 40:17.980
-SHORT?

40:19.068 --> 40:19.852
HOW SHORT?

40:19.982 --> 40:21.157
-20,000.

40:22.245 --> 40:24.509
-UNBELIEVABLE COINCIDENCE.

40:28.556 --> 40:29.992
-20,000. MITCH?

40:30.123 --> 40:31.603
-PAY OR PLAY. PAY OR PLAY.

40:31.733 --> 40:34.257
I HAD NO IDEA WHAT IT
MEANT UNTIL YESTERDAY.

40:34.388 --> 40:37.173
CAN YOU BELIEVE IT? HARVEY
FINALLY CAME THROUGH.

40:39.219 --> 40:40.742
-MITCH, YOU REALLY
NEED THIS MONEY.

40:40.873 --> 40:43.092
-NO, NO, IT'S OKAY. LOOK,
THE TRUCK IS RUNNING.

40:43.223 --> 40:45.268
HOBIE CAN PLAY HOCKEY.

40:45.399 --> 40:48.620
THESE GUYS WOULDN'T STAND A
CHANCE WITHOUT THIS PLACE.

40:50.796 --> 40:51.927
-THANK YOU.

40:58.630 --> 40:59.457
-I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO SAY.

41:00.675 --> 41:03.504
[SEA LION BARKING]
[LAUGHING]

41:06.638 --> 41:08.553
-YOU'RE A GOOD GIRL.
[SEA LION BARKING]

41:08.683 --> 41:11.164
YES, YOU'RE A GOOD GIRL.

41:11.294 --> 41:14.863
[MELLOW MUSIC]

41:31.401 --> 41:32.968
-HERE WE GO. EVERYBODY READY?

41:33.099 --> 41:35.580
COME ON, GILLY,
GET UP THERE. GO!

41:36.929 --> 41:38.408
[SPLASH]

41:38.539 --> 41:40.236
[SEA LION BARKING]

41:42.195 --> 41:43.718
[LAUGHS]

41:44.458 --> 41:45.328
-REALLY GREAT.

41:45.459 --> 41:46.591
-APPRECIATE IT.

41:49.681 --> 41:50.899
[SEA LION BARKING]

41:55.251 --> 41:56.731
[SEA LION BARKING]

41:57.950 --> 42:01.301
[MELLOW MUSIC]

42:08.917 --> 42:12.181
